1.3 \ul\b Scope\par
\ulnone\b0 Taxi cabs play an important role in sustainable transportation.The goal of the project If we are travelling in a new place or in emergency situations,Cab services will help you to reach your destination safely and on time.Reasonable price and 24/7 service also make cab service peoples favourite.\ul\b\fs40\par
