Overview\par
\ulnone\b0 Now a days people choose to travel via pre-booked cabs rather than catching a running taxi service.The approach in which drivers and customers are available on a single platform is  knows and cab service management system.This cab service management system  provides cab services online, and we find that booking a cab online at any time is more convenient.we can access its services through internet allows us to track our journeys or positions.\par
The system starts with entering details of driver and the passengers have to register with by entering  full name,mail id ,phone number and password.\par
Also the features like searching,online payment,cancellation of cab are also added.\par
\ul\b\par
